challengeInFlightExitInputSpent((bytes,u.notice: Challenges an exit from in-flight transaction input.

challengeInFlightExitNotCanonical((bytes.notice: Challenges an in-flight exit to be non canonical.

challengeInFlightExitOutputSpent((bytes,.notice: Challenges an exit from in-flight transaction output.

challengeStandardExit((uint160,bytes,byt.notice: Challenge a standard exit by showing the exiting output was spent.

getInFlightExitId(bytes).notice: Helper function to compute in-flight exit id.

getStandardExitId(bool,bytes,uint256).notice: Helper function to compute standard exit id.

inFlightExits(uint160).notice: Getter functions to retrieve in-flight exit data of the PaymentExitGame.

piggybackInFlightExitOnInput((bytes,uint.notice: Piggyback on an input of an in-flight exiting tx. Would be processed if the in-flight exit is non-canonical.

piggybackInFlightExitOnOutput((bytes,uin.notice: Piggyback on an output of an in-flight exiting tx. Would be processed if the in-flight exit is canonical.

processExit(uint160,uint256,address).notice: Callback processes exit function for the PlasmaFramework to call.

respondToNonCanonicalChallenge(bytes,uin.notice: Respond to a non canonical challenge by providing position and proving the correctness of it.

standardExits(uint160).notice: Getter functions to retrieve standard exit data of the PaymentExitGame.

startIFEBondSize().notice: Gets the in-flight exit bond size.

startInFlightExit((bytes,bytes[],uint256.notice: Starts withdrawal from a transaction that might be in-flight.

startStandardExit((uint192,bytes,bytes,b.notice: Starts a standard exit of a given output. Uses output-age priority.

startStandardExitBondSize().notice: Gets the standard exit bond size.

updatePiggybackBondSize(uint128).notice: Updates the piggyback bond size. Will take 2 days to come into effect.

updateStartIFEBondSize(uint128).notice: Updates the in-flight exit bond size. Will take 2 days to come into effect.

updateStartStandardExitBondSize(uint128).notice: Updates the standard exit bond size. Will take 2 days to come into effect.
